au.edu.rmit.agtgrp.apparate.jpathplan.entites

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.edu.rmit.agtgrp.apparate.jpathplan.entites.Edge

  • public abstract class Edge
extends Object
    An Edge interface is used to represent the information related to transition between the states. An application should provide at least the following information within an Edge. A start and an end Node for a transition with its associated cost. Additionally, an application can include the previous cost for a transition within an Edge, if the application models a dynamic environment.
    Author:
    Abhijeet Anand (abhijeet [dot] anand [at] rmit [dot] edu [dot] au)
